
Requirements.

1. polygator-linux version 1.1.9 and higher.

Installation.


1. Install polygator-linux kernel modules.

Compile and install from source directory by:

# make
# make install
# depmod

For K32 ISA boards is needed additional installation for sysvinit scripts:

# make sysvinit_install

2. Install ssconn

Compile and install from source directory by:

# ./configure --prefix=/usr --sysconfdir=/etc
# make
# make install

3. Usage

For start ssconn service daemon:

# ssconnctl start

For stop ssconn service daemon:

# ssconnctl stop

NOTE:
After installation ssconn started with default parameters.
All parameter list are shown by

# ssconn -h

For change ssconn parameters to non-default values you may edit ssconn arguments
in /etc/ssconn.conf file.
